but......in a week from ....dududuTODAY!!! something amazing happens and i dont know what im going to do. im seriously going to be the happiest/hottest person ever..k on the hottest thing i was totally jk. but still. i cant wait. at about 3 30 or so..wow. the transformation takes place and then at about 4 30....ill be a totally different person. im WAY stoked..likes wow. i cant believe how excited i am..wahoowahowootwoot.

peace out.

DogWood song....way sad...

I didn't die a natural death.
My life was stolen from me, before my first natural breath.
Casualty of circumstance.
Someone make a decision for me. 
They never gave me a chance. 

Chorus:
Where's that first birthday I hoped for?
The candle I'd blow out. 
No one will ever hear me laugh or ever see me smile.
I would've make my parents proud.

They weren't much more than children themselves.
I felt her honest reasons,
though she said it would further her health. 
I'm on the inside looking out.
Please don't just give up, at least give me to someone else.

(Chorus)

Adoption, abortion, am I responsible for your action? 
Life versus death, they make the choice, they let me go. 
Disregard human value.
What if your parents did this to you?
Victim of circumstance, this is our last dance.

Eleven weeks old today. 
My mother made a pro-choice, a purchase I would have to pay.
They found a price on my life. 
Consider this my farewell. My good bye.

in third period i started getting really hott and dizzy. i was sweating and i hate sweating..its gross. only boys should do that. but ya, so i was really hott and when i tried to get up to go to the bathroom i felt like i was about to fall over. but ihad to go p really bad so i had to go. i walked so slow there and back it took me forever to walk...well it felt like it. after class i couldnt even walked. my stomach started to hurt so bad and i was really shakey and dizzy. b ut i walked to the nurses office and took some tylonal and went home. were i went to bed. so iv been sleeping from 1 till 530 its great. im feeling alittle bit better. not as much dizzy just weak. like when my grandpa had cancer he was always weak and couldnt walk anywere not even across his house. i kinda feel like that. but i know he was in a worse condition than me. mine will go away soon...i hope. but atleast i didnt pass out at school...it really felt like if i were to stand up and walk i would just fall over and pass out..it was weird. i hated it. 

i hate chem. its sooo boring and the teacher is mean.

so many people from ncs were there, layman, veronica, carolyn(those two girls said..o hi, and then left...thats it!) and then sam and justin and adriane but they used to go there. and then i met cameron philips and this kid brandon...two awesome kids!
